messages.text: You sure you don’t want to just pick me up? ;)
It’s only the first time we’ll ever see each other in person
Good. Can’t wait to see you in real life. I’m sure the webcam doesn’t do you justice ;)
You know me too well lol
We’re just sitting here by the runway. I hope nothing’s wrong
It’s crowded in here. People everywhere. Nobody’s moving. They’re all standing around
That’s what people do in airports lol
You’re not desperately waiting for me at the arrivals? ;)
I’m sure you’re gonna be a while
But you’re not excited to see me for the first time?
Then won’t coffee make you extra excited? Maybe TOO excited ;)
We’re still just sitting here. People are getting upset
Are the flight attendants saying anything?
No, they look anxious about something though
It’s got to be a stressful job
Yeah, but their next flight would have to wait for them
I’m sure customs will take a while
If I ever get off this plane
You should have left later to pick me up
But I couldn’t wait any longer ;)
Has the plane moved at all yet?
Can you tell what’s going on?
Wait. I see some flashing lights out the window
Is there anything happening in there?
Just a lot of people standing around
A lot of frustrated people lol
wait - I just saw a handful of cops run by!
Do you see anything else out the window??
But the people in the rows ahead of me are looking out at something
I’m starting to get worried, Colin
I’m sure everything's ok - don't worry
I knew it! I knew that’s what you drink
Lol I told you a few times
I even drank one in front of you
I guess I missed it because of the time difference
A swat van just came up to our plane! Everybody’s starting to freak out
Not really. The stewardesses are trying to calm everybody down.
The passengers are all demanding to know what’s happening
Now there’s a bunch of banging and noises underneath the plane
Maybe they can tell me something
Is there a TV near you???
Yeah - they’re saying it’s a bomb scare!!!!
They know what they’re doing. They’ve been trained
What if I never get to see you in real life?
We've waited an entire YEAR for this moment
Just breathe. Everything’s going to be fine
What’s happening now?? On the inside??
They’re showing the bomb squad on TV climbing all over the plane
Talk to me Colin! I’m freaking out!!!
The air marshals just came on board and told us not to worry
There’s a lot going on down there it sounds like
Some people are on their phones calling loved ones
I see on TV that they’re bringing over one of those stair things for you guys to get off the plane
They’re telling us to get off
I’ll wait here by the coffee place
OMG NOW I SEE SMOKE COMING FROM THE PLANE ON TV!!!!!
Did you get off the plane?
Colin...if you are still reading these...
